column6: Sport Event has worked best for us with CPS of Rs. 179 which is lowest of all event types.
Conference as events has not performed well for us with CPS of Rs. 283 which is highest CPS among all event types.
Events held in Mumbai have performed well for us. It has CPS of Rs. 181 which is the lowest for any city.
Events held in Bengalore have not performed well for us. It has CPS of Rs. 255 which is the highest for any city.
